data.clean_description: Alprazolam Xanax is a prescription medicine that slows down the central nervous system. Xanax is as well recognized among the benzodiazepines. It is an anti-panic and anti-anxiety medication. Xanax is helpful to ease tenseness , nervousness , and worry related with nervousness disorders. It works by affecting the part of the brain that controls the emotions , thereby slowing down the nervous system. It has a fast onset of action and symptomatic relief and is mostly used as an anxiolytic drug commonly used to treat anxiety , panic attacks and insomnia. These are slow release tablets , which makes the effect last for a longer period. Produced by Pfizer Brand Xanax Blue Pentagons XR Extended release. Active ingredient Alprazolam Strength 2mg / tablet. Appearance. Blue pentagon shaped hard tablet , film - coated PU 66 imprint on one side , no imprint on other side. These are in lose packing , and comes as 50 tabs with 2 mg / tab.
data.name: Xanax, Pentagons XR from Pfizer, 2mg/tab - 50 tabs
